Package: liboglft-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
	liboglft1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: OpenGL-FreeType Library -- development files
 This C++ library supplies an interface between OpenType/TrueType fonts on your
 system and an OpenGL or Mesa application. It uses the excellent FreeType
 library to read font faces from their files and renders text strings as
 OpenGL primitives. 
 .
 This is the development package.

